<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.113277.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Magnolia brasiliensis A habit B immature gynoecium C immature fruit D bracts (perule) and gynoecium E details of trichomes on the fruit F specimen deposited in the RB herbarium showing coriaceous leaves. Photos: A-D: C. O. Azevedo; E: R. Mello-Silva 50 (RB 409806); F: L. M. Borges 393 (RB 664467)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/977394" ;
